{"tid":1672564,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"【陳同佳案】網民提議拍成電影 「少爺占」被點名做主角紅到台灣","createTime":"2019-10-24T07:35:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-02T11:41:05.000Z","uid":130626,"like":24,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"e99789b0758f45bc7ee5fa668f8230b2bde37828","tid":1672564,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T07:35:42.000Z","msg":"觸發反送中運動的台灣港女行李箱藏屍案疑兇陳同佳，因表示願意赴台自首，連日引發台港兩地政府「口水戰」。有網民提議，將該案拍成電影，更點名2位香港藝人擔任男主角。消息傳到台灣後，引起當地網民哄動，認為選角極神似。<br />\n有網民認為，此案件牽扯兩岸三地、兩性、宗教、政治與法律等話題，特別是陳同佳獲釋後聲稱會到台灣自首，坦言：「這一步步神轉折，太具有戲劇性了！」更有網民怱發奇想，如將事件拍成電影，究竟誰適合扮演陳同佳？有網民認為商台DJ「少爺占」以及在電影《點五步》中飾演「細威」一角走紅的演員胡子彤，都是合適人選。<br />\n少爺占在facebook回應：「今日突然有好多人都話我似邊個邊個，我覺得自己最似圖中（指他放在facebook的照片）呢個，哈哈!」<br />\n不過，也有網民認為，應對死者家屬予以尊重，不宜開拍有關電影。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191024/large/1571896637_2c21.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191024%2Flarge%2F1571896637_2c21.jpg&h=422567ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20191024/60189230\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191024%2F60189230&d=pzn6Hq8jxzH2PmSSbZvUod%2FmPfBwacFXLzUp2rw9Z8Q%3D&h=d5fb2b94\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191024%2F60189230&h=90431d4a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20191024/60189230</a>"},{"pid":"a8fc96b2623e87c617f04c4d041bdf03c82fd37c","tid":1672564,"uid":34777,"like":50,"dislike":0,"score":50,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T07:36:36.000Z","msg":"胡子彤似啲<br />\n個格似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a18853bbb1d291dc4e49e47984051db662830529","tid":1672564,"uid":4574,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"quote":{"pid":"a8fc96b2623e87c617f04c4d041bdf03c82fd37c","tid":1672564,"ui