","msg":"唔係好岩timing..."},{"pid":"3175702466d66718c596d58ff08cb44562c0ca9b","tid":1672564,"uid":10338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T07:59:32.000Z","msg":"邊個做林鄭？"},{"pid":"b819b0100dbd924b3c8ccb15b809a5fc76fd6999","tid":1672564,"uid":71508,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"3175702466d66718c596d58ff08cb44562c0ca9b","tid":1672564,"uid":10338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T07:59:32.000Z","msg":"邊個做林鄭？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T08:14:12.000Z","msg":"本人"},{"pid":"140f79bed619a751fe1e3a6c728e4cc4e65e9106","tid":1672564,"uid":8636,"like":14,"dislike":2,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"a8fc96b2623e87c617f04c4d041bdf03c82fd37c","tid":1672564,"uid":34777,"like":50,"dislike":0,"score":50,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T07:36:36.000Z","msg":"胡子彤似啲<br />\n個格似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T08:35:01.000Z","msg":"條撚樣賊眉賊眼係度扮型"},{"pid":"f57958c257e054f90ebeafe125daed8faed3122a","tid":1672564,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T08:57:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">中共斥巨資收賣西方<br />\n遊說集團統戰華盛頓</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n【華為被禁】華為遊說費飆60倍！原來聘用特朗普籌款人 欲說服白宮<br />\n<a href=\"https://china.hket.com/article/2479940?r=cpsdlc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchina.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2479940%3Fr%3Dcpsdlc&d=pzn6Hq8jxzH2PmSSbZvUod%2FmPfBwacFXLzUp2rw9Z8Q%3D&h=f7d810ee\" target=\"_blank\">https://china.hket.com/article/2479940?r=cpsdlc</a><br />\n<br />\n董建華基金會 擲2,240萬左右美政策<br />\n大搞政治游說 否認中共代理人<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171130/20230175\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171130%2F20230175&d=pzn6Hq8jxzH2PmSSbZvUod%2FmPfBwacFXLzUp2rw9Z8Q%3D&h=9dc67388\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171130%2F20230175&h=11b362ed\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171130/20230175</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">抗衡中國魔掌<br />\n組建香港既遊說團隊！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">誠意推薦：</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><em>香港大專學界國際事務代表團眾籌計劃</em></strong><br />\nHong Kong IAD Crowdfunding Plan<br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/hkiad-crowdfunding/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2Fhkiad-crowdfunding%2F&d=pzn6Hq8jxzH2PmSSbZvUod%2FmPfBwacFXLzUp2rw9Z8Q%3D&h=523dc39f\" target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/hkiad-crowdfunding/</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><em>香港眾志國際眾籌計劃 Demosisto International Campaign Crowdfunding Project</em></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E7%9C%BE%E7%B1%8C%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project/?show_desktop=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%259C%25BE%25E5%25BF%2597%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%25E7%259C%25BE%25E7%25B1%258C%25E8%25A8%2588%25E5%258A%2583-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project%2F%3Fshow_desktop%3D1&d=pzn6Hq8jxzH2PmSSbZvUod%2FmPfBwacFXLzUp2rw9Z8Q%3D&h=c6d53fe7\" target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E7%9C%BE%E7%B1%8C%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project/?show_desktop=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">什麼是遊說集團？</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">遊說集團的工作，<strong><ins>是嘗試影響立法者</ins></strong>或其他持份者決定或行為，在政治角力中為服務對象<strong><ins>爭取利益</ins></strong>。遊說集團的服務對象，可以是國家、企業、社會團體、個人。在美國，政治遊說是極為普遍及重要的一環；幾乎所有政治操作都有遊說集團的參與。</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">為什麼香港需要遊說隊伍？</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">任何國家的政治，背後都擁有複雜的政治脈絡；包括國家政策、政治形勢、民意、錯綜複雜的利益網絡、乃至個別官員或議員的性情喜好。要在國際社會維護和爭取香港的利益，<strong><ins>香港需要一支能具經驗和技巧，能夠有效收風、熟識政治形勢</ins></strong>、具備遊說策略的隊伍。</span>"},{"pid":"fb66a68736c9928ca8bba42dffd0ffc43300b00c","tid":1672564,"uid":282319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T09:24:01.000Z","msg":"少爺占仲入唔入到台灣？"},{"pid":"6b71a155bf84a3264eb1e61d7676aa09aba8ef73","tid":1672564,"uid":265694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a3fbd9fb2344636aad15afba276f96a629c8d9fa","tid":1672564,"uid":50901,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"e99789b0758f45bc7ee5fa668f8230b2bde37828","tid":1672564,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T07:35:42.000Z","msg":"觸發反送中運動的台灣港女行李箱藏屍案疑兇陳同佳，因表示願意赴台自首，連日引發台港兩地政府「口水戰」。有網民提議，將該案拍成電影，更點名2位香港藝人擔任男主角。消息傳到台灣後，引起當地網民哄動，認為選角極神似。<br />\n有網民認為，此案件牽扯兩岸三地、兩性、宗教、政治與法律等話題，特別是陳同佳獲釋後聲稱會到台灣自首，坦言：「這一步步神轉折，太具有戲劇性了！」更有網民怱發奇想，如將事件拍成電影，究竟誰適合扮演陳同佳？有網民認為商台DJ「少爺占」以及在電影《點五步》中飾演「細威」一角走紅的演員胡子彤，都是合適人選。<br />\n少爺占在facebook回應：「今日突然有好多人都話我似邊個邊個，我覺得自己最似圖中（指他放在facebook的照片）呢個，哈哈!」<br />\n不過，也有網民認為，應對死者家屬予以尊重，不宜開拍有關電影。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191024/large/1571896637_2c21.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191024%2Flarge%2F1571896637_2c21.jpg&h=422567ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20191024/60189230\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191024%2F60189230&d=pzn6Hq8jxzH2PmSSbZvUod%2FmPfBwacFXLzUp2rw9Z8Q%3D&h=d5fb2b94\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Freal